// program that is used with commercial off-set smokers to monitor, track 
// and keep a history of cooking temperatures 

// sensors will be located remotely and connected via wireless network
// data will be displayed via a web-based dashboard

// real-time data will show graphic analog thermometers.  
// Users will be able to set ranges that will be 
// represented by colors.

// all data will be sampled on a user selectable 
// period of time

// all data will be saved and available for review



